      title: 'How to Find Podcast Discussion Topics | Chaput',
      description: 'Find podcast topics by collecting real questions, useful tensions and contrasting viewpoints, then turn them into focused episode plans.',
      eyebrow: 'Podcast planning guide', h1: 'Find podcast topics with enough tension to carry an episode.',
